name: Rockstar Puppy Boutique
overview: Rockstar Puppy boutique has all the latest trends and fashion accessories for your small dog, which includes dog helmets, motorcycle dog carriers, dog houses and custom dog ID tags. Your dog should be able to cruise in the latest fashions, all while being safe. Rockstar Puppy has many designer custom ID tags. Those keep your pup tagged for identification and are great detail accessories. Is your furry friend a Harley rider or a sparkles diva? Rockstar Puppy has everything from birthdays and special occasions, to “just because.” Keeping your dog safe while on the back of a bike has never been easier with Rockstar Puppy’s dog carriers. They come in awesome colors and styles, so your options are endless; you think it- we can make it happen.
